---
title: Pork Chops with Cranberry Pan Sauce plus Spiced Roasted Carrots & Walnut-Raisin Couscous
description: Sweet-tangy-smoky combos are our jam, literally. These pan-seared pork chops are topped with a sauce that combines cranberry jam and smoky cinnamon paprika spice blend to stunning effect, offering a delightful contrast of flavors. Walnut-raisin couscous with shallots and smoky roasted carrots are also on hand to support all that deliciousness, coming together for a sophisticated dinner idea with fun textures and flavors for everyone.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-chops-with-cranberry-pan-sauce-9a485376.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/pork-chops-with-cranberry-pan-sauce-645127c3ca1206b185015021-22f100a9.pdf
servings: 2
time required: 40 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/pork-chops-with-cranberry-pan-sauce-645127c3ca1206b185015021
